        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Heightened gravity barely affects you thanks to your sturdy body. Ignore the effects of high and extreme gravity on your carrying capacity, falling damage, jumping distance, and Speed.</p>\n<p>You don't take bludgeoning damage every minute in extreme gravity. Additionally, while in high gravity, your first weapon Strike each round that uses a melee weapon that deals bludgeoning, slashing, or piercing damage gains a status bonus to damage equal to the number of weapon damage dice (or twice the number of weapon damage dice in extreme gravity).</p>"
